title: Was This Bert Show Member Taken Advantage Of After Being Abandoned With Her Friends Kids?
description:
Before she knew it, she was tricked into babysitting kids she didn’t even know.
Over the weekend, Keity’s best friend invited her to hang out with her and a friend. She thought it was going to be a peaceful girls’ day by the pool. But she ended up getting tricked into babysitting her friend’s kids for hours!
